==English==

===Noun===
'''intarweb'''

# {{slang}} ''Internet slang spelling of'' [[interweb]]
#:''Ha! Ha! I'm using TEH INTARWEB on a mac, cuz imma noob!!!1''

===Usage===
Usually used with [[leetspeak]] or other Internet slang spellings.

